; aWF_RT_Formule (aWRIRuleEngine) (Def Version:1) (Implem Version:1)
uses WFTypes, aWFRuleDesc
function Standard_Premium_Calculation(NAR : Num8) return tWFNum8 uses aWFStandAloneRule
var tmpRule : aWFRuleDesc
tmpRule = self.GetExactRuleToExecuteFromRankInRuleDesc(0, self.CurrentDate) if tmpRule <> Nil aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.MyOwner).AppendParam(NAR, 0, tmpRule) tmpRule.GetStandAloneResult(_Result, self) aWFStandAloneRule(tmpRule.MyOwner).CleanParamsAfterExecution(tmpRule) else self.AppendComment('No rule version defined at this date') endIf endFunc
procedure WFCalculate(inOut Result : tWFNum8) Result = self.Standard_Premium_Calculation(self.Cession__NAR) endProc

; aWF_RT_Formule (aWRIRuleEngine) (Def Version:1) (Implem Version:1)
procedure WFCalculate(inOut Result : Boolean) if self.Cession__FaceAmount >= 50000 Result = True self.AppendComment('This coverage is facultative because the Face Amount is greater or equal to 50K') else Result = False self.AppendComment('This coverage is not facultative because the Face Amount is lower than 50K') endIf endProc
